title: Completely taken down & brought back to life!
posting_body: ['Are you tired of renting & throwing away your money?', ' Get on the path to homeownership now!', "Really want to buy a home now, but you aren't quite ready to do that right now?", 'I can help you get on your path to home ownership now.', "Find a home that's on the market for sale, live in it and rent it now, and buy it when you're ready!", 'Perfect credit not needed!', 'Free credit repair consulting available.', 'Get into your DREAM HOME now!', "Rent it while you're getting ready to buy.", "You'll be able to buy it for a preset price.", "There are 100+'s of homes available in different areas & different prices available.", '3 different programs.', "Call me to learn more about a program that allows you to select a home that's for sale, rent it, and have the right to purchase that home at any time for a pre-set price.", 'We have helped thousands of people nationwide.', 'Get the details, call now!', 'Maria Martinez', 'show contact info', 'JPAR Realtors & Asscts', "This home is just an example of the 100's+ homes (in different areas & different prices) available through this awesome program.", ' Some terms & conditions apply']
